Andrew Kareba ni umwe mubanyamakuru bakomeye mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] bakorera icyigo k'igihugu cy'itangazamakuru

cyizwi nka RBA [[Rwanda|Rwanda broadcasting Agency]]

== Andrew Kareba ==
ni umwe mubanyamakuru b' abanyarwanda bakomeye mu intangaza makuru ryo mu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] bakorera 

ikigo k'igihugu cy'[[Rwanda|itangazamakuru]] RBA mubiganiro byinshi yagiye akora bitandukanye byamenyekanye cyane

mu [[Rwanda]] kandi akaba ari umwe mubanyamakuru bagira uruhare mwiterambere ry'urubyiruko abinyujije

mubiganiro agirana nabo kuri RBA.<ref>https://www.webrwanda.com/2020/07/umunyamakuru-wa-rba-andrew-kareba.html</ref>

== Uruhare ==
Andrew Kareba yamenyekanye cyane mu biganiro byiterambere ry'urubyiruko ndetse nku muntu wakunze cyane gufasha <ref>https://www.pinterest.com/pin/326440672995953230/</ref>

abana biga [[Uburezi mu Rwanda|mumashuri yisumbuye]] akabahuza n'ibyamamare bitandukanye ndetse nabantu bagiye biteza imbere 

muburyo butandukanye akabahuriza mu biganiro bigamije kubahugura ndetse no kubagira Inama mu buryo butandukanye

ndetse no kwiteza imbere.

== Ibiganiro ==
Umunyamakuru Andrew Kareba yakoze ibiganiro byinshi bitandukanye byatumye amenyekana cyane mu [[Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.flickr.com/photos/igihepictures/49035075312</ref>

harimio nka [[Rwanda|Insipire M]]<nowiki/>e yiganjemo ibiganiro byo gufasha urubyiruko cyane ndetse n'ikiganiro bita Wramutse [[Rwanda]]

kandi nubu akaba agikorera ikigo kigihugu cy'itangaza makuru mu [[Rwanda]]

== Indi mirimo ==
Andrew kandi uretse umwuga w'itangazamakuru kandi akora nibindi bintu byinshi bitandukanye harimo

nko kuba umuyobozi wibirori bitandukanye MC kuko

yamenyekanye kandi nka MC muri [[Nyampinga w'u Rwanda|Miss Rwanda]]<ref>https://www.webrwanda.com/2020/07/umunyamakuru-wa-rba-andrew-kareba.html</ref>

